00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:23,200
Please enjoy.

577
00:28:23,890 --> 00:28:24,740
It's fine.

578
00:28:24,740 --> 00:28:26,060
Let her try the new menu.

579
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:37,710
Florence,

580
00:28:38,370 --> 00:28:39,230
this oyster dish

581
00:28:39,230 --> 00:28:40,930
features tofu skin and Jinhua ham.

582
00:28:41,180 --> 00:28:42,820
It's a fusion of Chinese and Western.

583
00:28:43,130 --> 00:28:44,010
Please enjoy.

584
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,640
Here's the pan-seared snapper.

585
00:28:55,740 --> 00:28:57,260
It's paired with dill sauce,

586
00:28:57,800 --> 00:28:58,640
fish floss,

587
00:28:58,640 --> 00:28:59,450
and bamboo shoot sheaths.

588
00:28:59,490 --> 00:29:00,540
We prepared the sheaths

589
00:29:00,610 --> 00:29:02,340
using a unique Western technique.

590
00:29:02,550 --> 00:29:03,610
Plus, there's cream on the side.

591
00:29:03,780 --> 00:29:04,900
Hope you like it.

592
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:31,440
How is it?

593
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:35,300
She hasn't touched it?

594
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:40,820
Is she always like this?

595
00:29:43,060 --> 00:29:44,080
There was once.

596
00:29:44,220 --> 00:29:45,230
When my mother and her daughter

597
00:29:45,230 --> 00:29:46,860
did a piano duet here at Highland,

598
00:29:48,210 --> 00:29:49,270
she ate.

599
00:29:50,230 --> 00:29:51,080
Emily.

600
00:29:51,450 --> 00:29:53,370
That incredibly talented chef,

601
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:55,150
who later went back to China
to join relief efforts?

602
00:29:58,100 --> 00:29:58,970
Emily.

603
00:30:21,690 --> 00:30:22,770
Hello, Florence.

604
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:24,620
I'm the sous chef at Highland.

605
00:30:24,620 --> 00:30:25,470
My name's Liu Yan.

606
00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:27,460
I heard you're

607
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:29,010
Chef Emily's mother.

608
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:30,300
I just looked up

609
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:31,290
her social media.

610
00:30:31,860 --> 00:30:33,420
This is a tomato noodle dish

611
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:34,360
she recently developed.

612
00:30:34,930 --> 00:30:35,970
I did my best.

613
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:38,220
Please give it a try.

614
00:30:39,340 --> 00:30:40,900
You really look like my daughter.

615
00:30:43,300 --> 00:30:44,500
Yes, I saw

616
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:45,350
her pictures

617
00:30:45,350 --> 00:30:46,370
when I browsed...

618
00:30:48,540 --> 00:30:49,660
But the flavors

619
00:30:49,660 --> 00:30:50,700
might be different.

620
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:53,630
I haven't seen her in so long.

621
00:30:54,580 --> 00:30:56,520
I don't remember the taste of her food.

622
00:31:01,810 --> 00:31:02,680
Auntie,

623
00:31:03,300 --> 00:31:04,450
being a chef

624
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:05,870
is truly tough.

625
00:31:06,020 --> 00:31:07,620
Especially for those wanting

626
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:08,720
to help others through food,

627
00:31:09,940 --> 00:31:11,020
it's even harder.

628
00:31:11,820 --> 00:31:12,900
They're barely at home for years.

629
00:31:13,140 --> 00:31:14,230
But I believe,

630
00:31:15,260 --> 00:31:16,430
no matter where she is,

631
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:18,350
she absolutely

632
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:20,330
pours all her emotion

633
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:22,820
into her cooking.

634
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:24,180
That's her recipe.

635
00:31:25,420 --> 00:31:26,280
Maybe

636
00:31:26,280 --> 00:31:27,220
you'll find her presence

637
00:31:27,220 --> 00:31:28,220
in these noodles.

638
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:31,780
Enjoy your meal.

639
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:38,980
Don't go over.

640
00:32:40,460 --> 00:32:41,960
Just let Florence cry.

641
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:52,550
I think Highland should cook

642
00:32:52,550 --> 00:32:53,910
what the guests really want.

643
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:56,210
Even if it's not necessarily
what we excel at.

644
00:33:21,130 --> 00:33:21,990
Hello.

645
00:33:21,990 --> 00:33:22,930
Are you Liu Yan?

646
00:33:22,930 --> 00:33:24,300
Yeah, who is this?

647
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,020
Your mom, Jiang Fang,

648
00:33:26,120 --> 00:33:27,420
owes money to our casino.

649
00:33:28,010 --> 00:33:29,180
Come sort this out.

650
00:33:31,820 --> 00:33:32,830
Where's your casino?

651
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:53,030
Jiang Fang, right?

652
00:33:54,350 --> 00:33:55,320
What's your relationship?

653
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:56,750
- I don't know her.
- Mother and daughter.

654
00:34:00,020 --> 00:34:01,120
Did you bring enough money?

655
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:19,860
What did I tell you?

656
00:34:20,050 --> 00:34:21,600
Didn't I tell you not to answer?

657
00:34:22,650 --> 00:34:24,100
You gave them so much money.

658
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:25,890
Give it to me, I'd double it for sure!

659
00:34:27,070 --> 00:34:27,980
You're wasting money.

660
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:49,730
Stop following me!

661
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,980
Didn't I say this before?

662
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:55,410
Why do you interfere?

663
00:34:55,650 --> 00:34:57,210
Do I need you to save me?

664
00:35:02,730 --> 00:35:03,840
For all those years,

665
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,170
you had your life, and I had mine.

666
00:35:05,170 --> 00:35:06,500
Weren't we both doing fine?

667
00:35:18,570 --> 00:35:19,620
Stay away from me!

668
00:35:28,890 --> 00:35:29,780
Stop following me!

669
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:32,260
If you keep following me,

670
00:35:32,260 --> 00:35:33,110
I'll call the police!

671
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:37,420
You really have money to burn!

672
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:42,060
Go ahead, break your bones again!

673
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:44,100
You brought this on yourself!

674
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:52,320
Stop acting like
some devoted mother-daughter pair!

675
00:35:52,550 --> 00:35:53,820
Who said I care about you?

676
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:56,560
I haven't seen you in 13 years!

677
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:58,100
I feel nothing for you, understand?

678
00:35:58,540 --> 00:35:59,410
Such a drama queen!

679
00:36:06,460 --> 00:36:10,620
(Na Tcha Temple)

680
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:49,210
With the deities as my witness,

681
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:52,710
I, Jiang Fang, have burned incense

682
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:53,850
and prayed for over 20 years.

683
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:55,210
I've only ever asked for wealth.

684
00:36:57,370 --> 00:36:58,500
But today, that's not what I want.

685
00:37:00,050 --> 00:37:01,580
Today, I ask you to be my witness.

686
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:05,240
I, Jiang Fang, and Liu Yan,

687
00:37:06,490 --> 00:37:07,540
from now on,

688
00:37:09,330 --> 00:37:10,770
sever our mother-daughter ties.

689
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,080
No ties remain.

690
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,580
If I ever break this vow,

691
00:37:17,890 --> 00:37:19,020
may I be struck by lightning.

692
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:32,730
Jiang Fang!

693
00:37:39,730 --> 00:37:40,570
Take care.

694
00:37:42,470 --> 00:37:43,310
Stay safe.

695
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:07,660
(Jiang Fang & Liu Yan:
Sever mother-daughter ties)

696
00:38:52,250 --> 00:38:53,090
What's wrong?

697
00:39:01,900 --> 00:39:03,060
She wrote this for me.

698
00:39:10,690 --> 00:39:12,300
She chose gambling over me
completely this time.

699
00:39:15,100 --> 00:39:16,250
Are you even human?

700
00:39:16,390 --> 00:39:18,150
No, it's just a piece of paper.

701
00:39:18,150 --> 00:39:19,050
It has no legal effect.

702
00:39:19,050 --> 00:39:20,920
She signed it in front of Na Tcha.

703
00:39:21,300 --> 00:39:23,100
Even with Sun Wukong there,
it means nothing.

704
00:39:24,060 --> 00:39:25,190
You two are related by blood,

705
00:39:25,190 --> 00:39:26,460
and DNA can't be changed.

706
00:39:26,640 --> 00:39:27,650
And your mother-daughter status

707
00:39:27,650 --> 00:39:29,540
can't be erased by law.

708
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:30,990
Even if you could dissolve it,

709
00:39:30,990 --> 00:39:32,060
wouldn't that be

710
00:39:32,060 --> 00:39:32,910
a good thing?

711
00:39:34,690 --> 00:39:35,670
What do you mean?

712
00:39:35,670 --> 00:39:36,580
Can you

713
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:37,420
not joke right now?

714
00:39:42,710 --> 00:39:43,760
I think

715
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:47,570
you shouldn't deceive yourself.

716
00:39:48,130 --> 00:39:49,020
What do you mean?

717
00:39:49,150 --> 00:39:50,000
I've told you before.

718
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:51,390
If you truly want to help a gambler,

719
00:39:51,390 --> 00:39:52,760
the best way is to send them

720
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:54,210
to a gambling addiction center.

721
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:56,210
That place is like a prison.

722
00:39:56,210 --> 00:39:57,170
You've been there?

723
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:58,970
She can't handle it.

724
00:39:59,310 --> 00:40:01,290
Why can't she handle it?

725
00:40:03,230 --> 00:40:04,500
Or is it you who can't take it?

726
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:05,980
Afraid of being seen as unfilial?

727
00:40:06,170 --> 00:40:07,280
Scared people will say

728
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:08,350
you're not a good daughter?

729
00:40:08,690 --> 00:40:10,360
What's wrong with wanting to be filial?

730
00:40:10,600 --> 00:40:12,450
I want to be good to my own mother.

731
00:40:12,450 --> 00:40:13,390
Is that wrong?

732
00:40:13,390 --> 00:40:15,200
Being a pushover is meaningless.

733
00:40:17,080 --> 00:40:17,920
Why?

734
00:40:19,310 --> 00:40:20,240
Why must your words

735
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:21,480
be so harsh, Lu Tianchi?

736
00:40:21,810 --> 00:40:22,690
Yeah, you're right.

737
00:40:22,690 --> 00:40:23,500
I...

738
00:40:23,500 --> 00:40:24,990
My words are rough,
but the reasoning isn't.

739
00:40:25,130 --> 00:40:26,810
Why must you insist

740
00:40:26,810 --> 00:40:28,230
on dragging Jiang Fang back

741
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,350
into your life?

742
00:40:29,560 --> 00:40:30,610
Because in my life,

743
00:40:30,610 --> 00:40:32,500
I've never had
a normal emotional relationship.

744
00:40:34,930 --> 00:40:36,550
I just want to experience

745
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,350
what everyone else

746
00:40:39,200 --> 00:40:41,720
goes through every single day.

747
00:40:42,150 --> 00:40:43,310
Just something ordinary,

748
00:40:43,500 --> 00:40:46,140
real, and normal.

749
00:40:48,330 --> 00:40:49,490
I just want to live

750
00:40:49,490 --> 00:40:50,600
like a normal person.

751
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:52,410
What's wrong with that, Lu Tianchi?

752
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:56,500
Why is it that every time

753
00:40:56,500 --> 00:40:58,120
I try talking to you,

754
00:40:58,290 --> 00:40:59,810
you're either smirking

755
00:40:59,810 --> 00:41:00,700
or wearing

756
00:41:00,700 --> 00:41:02,490
this... attitude?

757
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:05,650
Anyway, I don't think

758
00:41:05,650 --> 00:41:06,810
you're abnormal.

759
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:31,140
Let me ask, are you sick?

760
00:41:32,430 --> 00:41:33,760
Go after her!

761
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:34,970
For what?

762
00:41:35,390 --> 00:41:36,350
What's the point?

763
00:41:37,040 --> 00:41:38,440
Should I just go and say,

764
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:39,680
"Sorry, my bad"? Then what?

765
00:41:39,950 --> 00:41:41,190
Let Jiang Fang keep fooling her?

766
00:41:41,190 --> 00:41:42,740
Who told you to talk about her mom?

767
00:41:42,740 --> 00:41:43,650
Then what should I say?

768
00:41:43,650 --> 00:41:44,650
She just poured her heart

769
00:41:44,650 --> 00:41:45,930
out to you.

770
00:41:45,930 --> 00:41:46,780
And you?

771
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:48,000
What? Mr. Enlightened?

772
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:49,280
Seeing through worldly illusions?

773
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,610
I was reasoning with her.

774
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:52,540
Was reason what she needed?

775
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:56,560
Lu Tianchi,

776
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:58,850
don't you understand?

777
00:41:59,750 --> 00:42:01,070
When she said she wants

778
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:02,690
a normal emotional relationship,

779
00:42:03,420 --> 00:42:04,610
did she mean only Jiang Fang?

780
00:42:06,330 --> 00:42:07,550
Or is it about you, too?

781
00:42:09,060 --> 00:42:10,160
Let me ask you something.

782
00:42:11,460 --> 00:42:12,830
If you really lose her,

783
00:42:13,810 --> 00:42:14,940
would it be worth it?

784
00:42:18,380 --> 00:42:19,250
Liu Yan!

785
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:24,560
Liu Yan.

786
00:42:26,060 --> 00:42:26,970
Liu Yan!

787
00:42:29,990 --> 00:42:30,940
Liu Yan.

788
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,860
Don't stay in the ocean

789
00:42:37,090 --> 00:42:37,930
this late!

790
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:39,080
Get out of there!

791
00:42:39,750 --> 00:42:40,590
Liu Yan!

792
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:45,810
I need to talk to you.

793
00:42:45,810 --> 00:42:46,810
Please, just come up.

794
00:42:48,950 --> 00:42:50,500
It's dangerous! Too dark!

795
00:42:50,830 --> 00:42:51,750
Stop swimming, okay?

796
00:42:51,750 --> 00:42:53,500
I can't swim. Can you come up?

797
00:42:57,610 --> 00:42:58,560
Too dark!

798
00:42:58,560 --> 00:42:59,800
Please come up!

799
00:43:04,170 --> 00:43:05,960
Come back. I really can't swim!

800
00:43:08,770 --> 00:43:09,660
I...

801
00:43:14,810 --> 00:43:15,690
Liu Yan!

802
00:43:21,740 --> 00:43:23,410
Wait, can I live with you?

803
00:43:25,700 --> 00:43:26,860
I'll rent a two-bedroom place.

804
00:43:27,900 --> 00:43:28,910
That way, Li Zan

805
00:43:28,910 --> 00:43:30,020
can have his own room!

806
00:43:32,260 --> 00:43:33,480
You cook,

807
00:43:34,060 --> 00:43:35,140
and I'll handle the dishes.

808
00:43:38,050 --> 00:43:39,690
Can you please come back first?

809
00:43:41,830 --> 00:43:43,690
Can you even hear me?

810
00:43:47,770 --> 00:43:49,290
Why are you yelling at the sea?

811
00:43:52,010 --> 00:43:54,330
Weren't you just over there?

812
00:43:56,930 --> 00:43:58,620
That's a reef, man!

813
00:44:00,020 --> 00:44:01,770
So, did you hear me or not?

814
00:44:02,260 --> 00:44:03,760
Try talking underwater yourself.

815
00:44:03,760 --> 00:44:04,730
Can you hear anything?

816
00:44:05,810 --> 00:44:06,730
No sound at all?

817
00:44:07,800 --> 00:44:08,640
You try it.

818
00:44:09,370 --> 00:44:11,130
Wait, I can't swim.

819
00:44:11,130 --> 00:44:11,980
Could you

820
00:44:11,980 --> 00:44:12,900
pull me back a little?

821
00:44:13,160 --> 00:44:14,410
If you can't swim,

822
00:44:14,880 --> 00:44:15,980
why recklessly show off?

823
00:44:16,070 --> 00:44:17,250
I was looking for you!

824
00:44:20,160 --> 00:44:21,000
Give me a hand.

825
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:22,850
You're too heavy!

826
00:44:26,440 --> 00:44:27,370
Can't swim...

827
00:44:59,030 --> 00:44:59,890
You're from Shanghai,

828
00:44:59,890 --> 00:45:00,850
how come you can't swim?

829
00:45:01,120 --> 00:45:02,200
Since when must

830
00:45:02,200 --> 00:45:03,350
a person from Shanghai swim?

831
00:45:04,270 --> 00:45:05,130
Turn off the light.

832
00:45:32,030 --> 00:45:32,870
I can't sleep.

833
00:45:33,020 --> 00:45:33,860
Why?

834
00:45:34,500 --> 00:45:35,980
The bed shakes when you move!

835
00:45:38,370 --> 00:45:39,210
Sorry.

836
00:45:41,640 --> 00:45:42,660
Why aren't you asleep?

837
00:45:45,330 --> 00:45:47,230
The bed shakes when I move.

838
00:45:55,790 --> 00:45:56,630
Good night.

839
00:46:35,980 --> 00:46:37,340
Lu Tianchi, what are you doing?

840
00:46:44,840 --> 00:46:45,880
What are you doing?

841
00:46:46,970 --> 00:46:49,460
I'm testing if you can hear

842
00:46:49,460 --> 00:46:51,460
outside sounds underwater.

843
00:46:53,150 --> 00:46:54,260
It's perfect you're here.

844
00:46:54,370 --> 00:46:55,540
I'll go under again.

845
00:46:55,540 --> 00:46:57,440
Say something

846
00:46:57,660 --> 00:46:58,540
after my signal.

847
00:47:10,480 --> 00:47:11,460
Can you hear me?

848
00:47:12,300 --> 00:47:13,500
Lu Tianchi, can you hear me?

849
00:47:22,180 --> 00:47:23,100
Did you hear that?

850
00:47:28,020 --> 00:47:29,160
So... you heard

851
00:47:29,160 --> 00:47:30,140
everything I said

852
00:47:35,660 --> 00:47:36,740
in the ocean?

853
00:47:46,910 --> 00:47:50,740
♪My true heart♪

854
00:47:51,530 --> 00:47:55,500
♪Longing for true love♪

855
00:47:56,180 --> 00:48:00,070
♪Love left me completely broken♪

856
00:48:00,070 --> 00:48:05,520
♪Why do sweet dreams fade so fast♪

857
00:48:25,290 --> 00:48:29,260
♪Your gentle eyes always draw me in♪

858
00:48:29,970 --> 00:48:33,940
♪And your kind heart truly understands♪

859
00:48:34,930 --> 00:48:36,770
♪If you're willing♪

860
00:48:37,300 --> 00:48:39,050
♪Let me come closer to you♪

861
00:48:39,340 --> 00:48:43,270
♪I know someday,
you'll see my true heart♪

862
00:48:44,110 --> 00:48:48,220
♪Stars shine bright, wind sighs low♪

863
00:48:48,870 --> 00:48:53,080
♪A maiden's heart feels lone and woe♪

864
00:48:53,590 --> 00:48:55,640
